\u51fb\\u89c2\\u770b\\u5fae\\u8bfe\",\"file_src\":\"\\/Public\\/Upload\\/\\/book\\/video\\/2018-02-03\\/5a754d8464273.mp4\",\"is_head\":\"0\"}]',0,1517636949,1517637000),('8c0586181576f0361f1b08b0494721fd','9d4517d18f3d102363c6cb7fefc310c8','/Public/Upload//book/img/2018-02-12/5a81b2da30013.jpg','&lt;p&gt;钱文忠&lt;/p&gt;','钱文忠解读弟子规',2,'&lt;p&gt;《弟子规》是一本只有一千来字的小册子，儒家思想提倡的孝、悌、谨、信、泛爱众、亲仁和余力学文等思想，都在《弟子规》中，有明确的行为规范，那么这些行为规范，对于现代人会有什么作用呢？《弟子规》为什么会引起许多现代人的重视？《弟子规》的作者是谁？成书于哪个年代？其中都有哪些严格的规定？又是什么原因，使越来越多的人，开始学习《弟子规》呢？&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','[{\"type\":\"audio\",\"title\":\"01 \\u89c4\\u77e9\\u7684\\u4f5c\\u7528\",\"file_src\":\"\\/Public\\/Upload\\/\\/book\\/audio\\/2018-02-12\\/5a81b4d29893f.mp3\",\"is_head\":\"0\"},{\"type\":\"audio\",\"title\":\"02 \\u5165\\u5219\\u5b5d1\",\"file_src\":\"\\/Public\\/Upload\\/\\/book\\/audio\\/2018-02-12\\/5a81b55c9531c.mp3\",\"is_head\":\"0\"},{\"type\":\"audio\",\"title\":\"03 \\u5165\\u5219\\u5b5d2\",\"file_src\":\"\\/Public\\/Upload\\/\\/book\\/audio\\/2018-02-12\\/5a81b57addc4b.mp3\",\"is_head\":\"0\"},{\"type\":\"audio\",\"title\":\"04 \\u5165\\u5219\\u5b5d3\",\"file_src\":\"\\/Public\\/Upload\\/\\/book\\/audio\\/2018-02-12\\/5a81b59b1b51c.mp3\",\"is_head\":\"0\"},{\"type\":\"audio\",\"title\":\"05 \\u5165\\u5219\\u5b5d4\",\"file_src\":\"\\/Public\\/Upload\\/\\/book\\/audio\\/2018-02-12\\/5a81b5af731ef.mp3\",\"is_head\":\"0\"},{\"type\":\"audio\",\"title\":\"06 \\u51fa\\u5219\\u608c1\",\"file_src\":\"\\/Public\\/Upload\\/\\/book\\/audio\\/2018-02-12\\/5a81b5ca362b6.mp3\",\"is_head\":\"0\"},{\"type\":\"audio\",\"title\":\"07 \\u51fa\\u5219\\u608c2\",\"file_src\":\"\\/Public\\/Upload\\/\\/book\\/audio\\/2018-02-12\\/5a81b5e0d2a49.mp3\",\"is_head\":\"0\"},{\"type\":\"audio\",\"title\":\"08 \\u8c281\",\"file_src\":\"\\/Public\\/Upload\\/\\/book\\/audio\\/2018-02-12\\/5a81b5f9b433f.mp3\",\"is_head\":\"0\"},{\"type\":\"audio\",\"title\":\"09 \\u8c282\",\"file_src\":\"\\/Public\\/Upload\\/\\/book\\/audio\\/2018-0